data.description: Must see! Traditional, all-brick 3 BDM/2 BA home centrally located in an established neighborhood in Temple, near restaurants, shopping, schools and parks. The home offers a cozy living room with ceiling fans and multiple large windows that allow an abundance of natural light. The kitchen's beautiful oak cabinetry offers ample storage and features white appliances. A separate, formal dining area with accent wall allows for entertaining as well as family dinners. The primary bedroom has carpet, ceiling fans and an en suite bathroom with tiled accents, step in shower and single vanity. Two guest bedrooms share the second bath which has a shower/tub combo and tiled single vanity. Two car garage has storage/hobby room. The home has a NEW ROOF!! Relax on the covered back patio overlooking the large, fully fenced backyard with mature trees. Come see this lovely home today!
